Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's going to be hot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you hot wearing all those clothes during the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?  Isn't that the newspaper from three days ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say there was a murder in Verden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that the murderer was a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to Verden, too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a friend there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'll see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:18.99,Monster-Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(647,785)\fad(840,800)\1c&HFCFCFC&\3c&H000000&\3a&H66&\fs100\bord0.4\shad1.6\b1}{\4c&HFCFCFC&}{\t(0,1640,\4c&H000000&)}{\t(3050,4050,\4c&HFCFCFC&)}Elderly Soldier and A Young Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:56.02,Location,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(652,780)\fad(730,730)}Kiesen Police Station
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:56.02,Location,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,980)\fad(730,730)\fs48}(Germany)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're from the foreigner division of the French army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:03:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You became a mercenary in 1979.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You participated in the war in Nicaragua.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From 1981 to 1984, you aided the Anti-Government Guerillas in Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In 1987, you played an integral part in the secret plan to assassinate the Mossad Islamic leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an excellent battle record,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hugo Bernhardt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mercenaries like you usually hold seminars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably produce excellent students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would love it if our young ones could attend one of your lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this man a good student?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should have appeared before you about five months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a genius with a scalpel, but how was he with a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like to talk about my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:49.89,Location,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(635,735)\fad(700,700)\fscy130}5 Months Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has anyone ever taught you how to use a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you learn by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never used one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not once?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is an unreasonable request,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but... you're the only person I can ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When people ask for my help, I tell them to forget all the experience they've had with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've had someone with no experience come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:06:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how you start, whether you have experience or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it as well as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always watch over those who are training in place of the instructor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to stare at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A brambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she looking for food for her chicks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you so tired that you've lost your appetite?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:09:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating is part of the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she your daugh...  No, I mean, granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shot and killed her mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right in front of her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was in Myanmar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into a jungle village and they were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mother had a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had waited one more second, I would have been shot and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how I ended up with that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't smiled once since we started living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll probably hate me for the rest of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens when you hold a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then don't hold a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of Daphne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're done, come to the back pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?  Two shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you fire a gun, always fire twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you fire twice, the probability that you will deliver the finishing blow increases by a hundred times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then it's as if you've just been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always preparing food for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I made Japanese food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's meat and potato stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you'll like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cut down a tree and made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would make it feel more Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at using chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A brambling chick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It fell out of its nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you have to put it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult for them to survive away from their nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost impossible to raise them that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with its mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is decided within three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hesitate, you'll be the one shot and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what were his grades when he graduated?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He received full points for skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He received a passing grade for endurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His concentration was exceptional.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting someone is a completely different thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether a person shoots first or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is where the road splits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The road that decides whether you can use a gun or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to tell me if you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking care of me these last five months.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the payment for the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please eat the meat and potato stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damm it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She smiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know where he is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
